{"id":14698,"date":"2013-06-12T20:39:10","date_gmt":"2013-06-12T16:39:10","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=14698"},"modified":"2019-05-15T18:47:09","modified_gmt":"2019-05-15T14:47:09","slug":"romans-five-good-traits","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/12\/romans-five-good-traits\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Byzantines: The Romans have five good qualities in them"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Al-Mustawrid reported: He said in front of Amr ibn al-&#8216;As that he heard the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, say, \u201c<b>The Hour will be established while the Romans are the majority of people.<\/b>\u201d Amr said, \u201cBe careful what you say.\u201d He said, \u201cI have said what I heard from the Messenger of Allah.\u201d Amr said, \u201cIf the Prophet said that, indeed, there are four good qualities in them: they are the most forbearing of people in tribulation, they are the quickest to recover after a calamity, they are the most eager to return after a retreat, and they are good to the poor, the orphan, and the vulnerable. Their fifth quality is good and beautiful: they are the best at stopping the oppression of their kings.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2898<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <b><i>Sahih<\/i><\/b> (authentic) according to Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0631\u0650\u062f\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0631\u064e\u0634\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0639\u0650\u0646\u0652\u062f\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0648 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0635\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0645\u0650\u0639\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u